{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457780/extras/topo.png?t=1738445285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PREPARE TO DIE!</strong><br>In <i>Bone n' Gone</i>, you control a fragile and determined skeleton, ready to defeat the bosses that plague areas perfectly designed for smooth action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LOW HEALTH? HIGH REWARD!</strong><br>Be rewarded for risky gameplay, as you deal more damage the less health you have! But be careful, death can be pretty harsh at times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457780/extras/logo_Sigla.png?t=1738445285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BREATHTAKING SCENARIOS</strong><br>With retro graphics, you\u2019ll admire every detail and carefully placed texture in the game. Featuring references to classic games, we guarantee an interesting gameplay experience with stunning visuals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457780/extras/baixo.png?t=1738445285\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WHO WE ARE</strong><br>Gatocalvojogos is here to add to the market's lineup of challenging shooters. With authentic, AI-free art and horrendously passionate code, we\u2019re here to stay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457780/extras/gato_calvo_name.png?t=1738445285\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3457780?t=1738445285","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3457780?t=1738445285","capsule_image":"https://shared.akam